# Test-suite relaxations on top of the root config.
# - use-anonymous-namespace fires on doctest's TEST_CASE expansion
# - c-arrays / pi-literals / enum sizes are deliberate in test vectors
# - positional aggregate init mirrors SEQUENCE wire order in test vectors
---
InheritParentConfig: true
Checks: >
  -misc-use-anonymous-namespace,
  -modernize-avoid-c-arrays,
  -modernize-use-designated-initializers,
  -modernize-use-std-numbers,
  -performance-enum-size
